Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:10.98,Title1,Sign 0208,0000,0000,0000,,My Boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gouda Takeo, a first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's my friend, Sunakawa Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:20.49,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him since we were three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:29.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring in Japan, but I'm \Nexperiencing spring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:38.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,After all, for the first time in \Nmy life, I have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Spring's awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:57.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's just helping you get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like I did anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You were a huge help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.09,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, you're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This year's spring is the true spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You made these, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to try making Japanese \Nsweets for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought these cherry blossom petal \Nshapes and stuff were cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.13,SignA,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(188,1)} You're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're great at making Japanese sweets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me so happy when \Nyou say that, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I really like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's springtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Spring's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I was thinking the same thing, too.
