Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, summer's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Fall has its own charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like winter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I like winter.
