Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.70,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.41,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.96,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-paper-scissors time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:21.69,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:22.51,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Only four can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.46,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A singles' meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I probably won't talk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.55,SignA,Sign 0733,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}I'll ruin the mood
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There may be a nice girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're Yamato's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They must all be great girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just because someone's friends \Nwith a nice person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean they're nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:52.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, they're friends because the \Nperson's nice enough to have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What you said just now was really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:09.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, they're the friends who'll be \Ncoming to the singles' meet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're all cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling really shy about \Nintroducing you to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.10,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:21.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's always herself, no matter where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:24.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamato, Takeo-kun's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:31.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The other girls here are all friends from my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.07,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.06,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.45,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're all cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.33,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,So who's Rinko's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.07,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,This girl talks about her boyfriend every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:45.46,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what people call what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.10,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takeo-kun, my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.11,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,A bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.86,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just as tall as Rinko said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.61,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,I almost mistook you for a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:06.48,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just like Rinko said, you have big hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.24,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I almost mistook you for a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.98,EyecatchA,Sign 0908,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4A5BE4&}Salmon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.48,EyecatchB,Sign 0910,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD749DA&}Singles' Meet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.86,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.86,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You were lighter than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.83,Default - italics,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,He's way too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:32.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to leave boxes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll move them out of the way, \Nso people can pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.84,Default - italics,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.37,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency exit's locked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.85,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should tell the restaurant staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:48.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing should be reported to the \Nmanagement company, not the restaurant staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.53,Default - italics,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Suna, you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.76,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, is that one of the bear's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:53.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.74,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.74,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's order drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.31,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants orange juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.24,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.18,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,I want coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.12,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,The more you look at him, the hotter he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.47,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But he isn't talking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.55,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try talking to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.80,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,You go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you make the reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:08.64,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.61,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I actually thought he had to be Rinko's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You did a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.55,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she went for the bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.63,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.83,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, your girlfriend's real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.58,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.50,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad for you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:25.52,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And why does everyone like \Nher boyfriend so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.59,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,We should toss you in the air again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.68,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's aim for three tosses next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.52,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.53,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got their drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.40,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's start with a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.51,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we don't have a bottle opener.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.15,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.53,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.91,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you opened it with your bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.95,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.02,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.92,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.83,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, that isn't how you're \Nsupposed to open them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.79,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you all attend an \Nall-girls' high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.33,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have any guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.24,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.67,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask Yamato's friends stupid questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.84,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not do them any wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.88,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.91,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,So none of you girls has a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:16.69,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.56,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any opportunities to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.82,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, none.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:23.04,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're co-ed, but we don't \Nhave any opportunities, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.92,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, none.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.25,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls go for the popular guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.96,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,If there are any, there's only our school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.36,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.83,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go to that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.80,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.14,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.21,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Our last festival in junior high, we ran a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.06,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,A café ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.47,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,What was your getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.46,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that question's super dated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.09,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, can I come sit with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run a café, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:45.92,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.97,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, let's swap seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I baked stuff for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I made a lot of pound cake in different flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I would've liked to have tried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bake some for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if you \Nate a whole cake in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.37,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops, my contact lens shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.25,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll go fix it in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.99,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako and Ayu still haven't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.02,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He's way too tall, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.35,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.36,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's the boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.36,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He's barely human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.11,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko kept going on about how cool he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.29,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought he must be this hottie, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.30,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I almost had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.59,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.45,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have the guts to be seen with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.26,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just because someone's friends \Nwith a nice person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.14,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean they're nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.14,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,And she says he's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.74,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Rinko's right in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.04,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.26,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:30.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:55.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My friends said mean things \Nabout you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they hurt your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings are just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There are all kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's because there are all kinds of people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,that I was able to meet you, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.55,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like seeing you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:45.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I found out that you've been saying really \Nnice things about me to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:58.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really like you a lot, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I bet I just didn't explain very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been so vague,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,they didn't get how cool you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When I go back, I'll try to explain it in \Na way that's easier to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:25.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They just don't know the real you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:33.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, I'm thankful that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope things can stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.79,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I called the fire department when \Na fire suddenly broke out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.42,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but they're not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:52.82,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.76,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find Nanako and Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.18,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't come back from the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.18,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,They're still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring them out, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.48,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:11.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I will save your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.72,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.00,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.42,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.00,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.00,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:35.74,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I... feel like I was carried out... \Nby a really strong wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.27,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:47.34,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You looked really happy in the \Nphoto you sent my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're all good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.85,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.78,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in th—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.92,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.09,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:24.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.53,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the firefighters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.36,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.06,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.88,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,But your boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.24,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,H-He might be in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.23,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me and got left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:45.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is really it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:51.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've been too happy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.01,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.60,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I can die helping you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.95,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,it isn't such a bad way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,My cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it still has a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:23.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yamato-san's this close \Nto jumping into the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me go to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've grasped the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,can you get back here ASAP?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Life's pretty boring for me, too, \Nif you aren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takeo-ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.23,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.49,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:00.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when you cry, more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:08.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:26.87,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Yamato happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:47.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:51.56,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I will never make you cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.09,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.85,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.98,SignB,Sign 2009,0000,0000,0000,,Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:11.59,Default - italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.01,Default - italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the suspension bridge effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:13.84,Default - italics,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.98,Default - italics,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,He's not my type at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so I think I wasn't clear enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,about how cool Takeo-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:26.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to try to explain in a \Nway that's easier to understand—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.53,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Rinko. We got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.77,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.35,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.53,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.28,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,And you're awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.15,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't steal him from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.38,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,No way we would!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.82,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's no way we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:44.48,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He only has eyes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:49.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling the only way \Nyou'd die is from old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:55.02,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Takeo's really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:55.96,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling major respect all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.18,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.79,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, toss him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.35,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.67,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, thank you so much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:16.46,Phone,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(1,1936)}Yamato Rinko  \NSubject: Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.37,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone understands why \Nyou're a good person now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.29,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You were super cool today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.50,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If you became a firefighter or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.34,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd do a lot of good work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:22.07,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,even though I'd get worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.03,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Night, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.30,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.27,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Spring's great, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Title2,Sign 2247,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,515)}I'm Dense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:49.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: I'm Dense.
